[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 3.7"]]
[[!pagetemplate template="news.tmpl"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes that affect Tails 3.7 are now fixed in Tails 3.7.1.

We **strongly** encourage you to
[[upgrade to Tails 3.7.1|news/version_3.7.1]] as soon as possible.

 - Tor Browser: [[!mfsa 2018-14]]
 - Thunderbird: [[!debsa2018 4209]]
 - cURL: [[!debsa2018 4202]]
 - GnuPG (modern): [[!debsa2018 4222]]
 - GnuPG (legacy): [[!debsa2018 4223]]
 - Git: [[!debsa2018 4212]]
 - PackageKit: [[!debsa2018 4207]]
 - procps: [[!debsa2018 4208]]
 - wavpack: [[!debsa2018 4197]]
 - wget: [[!debsa2018 4195]]
 - xdg-utils: [[!debsa2018 4211]]
